#&quot;Barren Egg&quot; (Eaton, Sobule) – 3:37
#&quot;Half a Heart&quot; (DeMain, Sobule) – 3:47
#&quot;When My Ship Comes In&quot; (Eaton, Marvin Gaye, Ivy Jo Hunter, Sobule, William Stevenson) – 3:50
